### **3. 26_LogSpikeScanner**  
**Description:**  
Parses log files and detects spikes, repetition loops, and keyword-based warnings.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogSpikeScanner - Burst & Frequency Log Analyzer

LogSpikeScanner simplifies incident detection by identifying log anomalies and activity surges.

## Features
- Spike and repetition detection  
- Heatmap clustering  
- CLI output for devops  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_LogSpikeScanner.git
cd 26_LogSpikeScanner
python analyze.py logs/system.log
